@Reasoning:
"pat as name" binds the matched value to a name in addition to whatever sub-bindings the pattern produces; HIR AsPattern records both the inner pattern and the binding name so the matcher emits the extra binding.
@End Reasoning
Process called "translate_as_pattern" takes translator as Integer, fsharp_node as Integer returns Integer:
    Note: Translate F# as pattern to HIR as pattern

    Let children be proc memory_get_int64 from Layout with fsharp_node, 16
    Let child_count be proc memory_get_int64 from Layout with fsharp_node, 24

