        proc set_translation_error with translator, "As pattern requires pattern and variable"
        Return 0
    End If

    Note: The canonical pattern surface has no dedicated as-pattern kind; an
    Note: as-pattern is a variable binding whose match additionally constrains
    Note: the value, so it is represented as HIR_IDENTIFIER_PATTERN (the binding
    Note: pattern kind) carrying [inner pattern, variable pattern] as children
