    While i is less than child_count:
        Let child_node be proc list_get from List with children, i
        Let hir_child be proc translate_declaration with translator, child_node
        If hir_child is not equal to 0:
            proc add_hir_node from HIR with hir_node, hir_child
        End If
        Set i to i plus 1
    End While

    Return hir_node
End Process

@Reasoning:
F# namespaces are top-level partitioning (cannot nest values directly, only types and modules); HIR NamespaceDeclaration enforces this contract by accepting only module and type children, distinct from ModuleDeclaration which also accepts values.
@End Reasoning
Process called "translate_namespace_declaration" takes translator as Integer, fsharp_node as Integer returns Integer:
